From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 09:26:25 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 25/84] Load PDF viewer resources

A viewer knocks at the pak-file door,
Finds index.html on the resource-store.
No streams, no guests, no render show,
Just bytes where future PDFs go.
---
 content/libtermsurf_chromium/BUILD.gn         |  2 +
 .../extensions/ts_pdf_resource_bundle.cc      | 67 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../extensions/ts_pdf_resource_bundle.h       | 16 +++++
 .../libtermsurf_chromium/ts_main_delegate.cc  |  8 +++
 .../libtermsurf_chromium/ts_main_delegate.h   |  1 +
 5 files changed, 94 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 content/libtermsurf_chromium/extensions/ts_pdf_resource_bundle.cc
 create mode 100644 content/libtermsurf_chromium/extensions/ts_pdf_resource_bundle.h

